OL,7,     Ffrom Manchester, Gail from West
OL,8,     FYorkshire, Harry from Plymouth and
OL,9,     FMaddy from Gloucester pit their
OL,10,     Fwits against one of the ruthless
OL,11,     FChasers in the hope of winning a
OL,12,     Fpotential prize pot worth
OL,13,     Fthousands of pounds. They work as
OL,14,     Fa team and play strategically to
