OL,5,G2350 Twisted Twins
OL,6,     FDocumentary exploring the stories
OL,7,     Fof identical twins involved in
OL,8,     Fcases of murder, manslaughter or
OL,9,     Fmissing persons. Lyn Dawson had
OL,10,     Fbeen missing for more than 35
OL,11,     Fyears when an investigative
OL,12,     Fpodcast led to the case being
OL,13,     Freopened and her husband Chris
OL,14,     FDawson being accused of murder. He
OL,15,     Fhad wanted to start a new life
OL,16,     Fwith his teenage lover, a
OL,17,     Frelationship seemingly condoned by
OL,18,     Fhis identical twin Paul, who
OL,19,     Fcontinues to support him to this
OL,20,     Fday
